# TradingApp Project Context

- You are an expert quantitative developer building a trading system application with the latest software.
- Implement TradingView lightweight charts to display realtime data (e.g. MSFT), with 12 months of data across 5m, 15m, 30m, 1h, 4h, 8h, and 1d timeframes.
- Data is sourced from the IB Gateway.
- Use this tradingapp project as the base to expand on further.
- The application runs remotely only; there are no dependencies installed locally.
